Package aom.scripting.ui.config

Class EngineConfig

Object
EngineConfig
public class EngineConfig
extends Object
This class provides an overview of Configs related to the game engine (a.k.a. BANG).
Author:
Mythic_Freak - mythic.freak[a]gmail.com
